HEADWORD: Lords and Ladies
<hw>Lords" and La"dies</hw> <pr>(?)</pr> <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Bot.)</fld>
<def>The European wake-robin (<spn>Arum maculatum</spn>), -- those with
purplish spadix the lords, and those with pale spadix the ladies.</def>
<rj><au>Dr. Prior.</au></rj>⟦br⟧
